input[type="text"] 
{
	border : 2px solid red;
}
둘다 하게되면 속성값으로 만든 가중치가 높다
첫번째 요소 
input:first-of-type
{
	border : 2px solid green;
}  */

	input:lost-of-type{border : 2px solid blue;}
	input:nth-child(5){border : 2px solid green;}
	input:nth-last-child(2){border : 2px solid yellow;}
	input:last-child{border : 2px solid black;}
	input:disable{border : 2px solid cyan;}
	

